OL,3,CIconic costume from Christmas film Elf
OL,4,Cexpected to fetch up to #200,000
OL,6,FA costume worn by Will Ferrell on the
OL,7,Fbeloved Christmas film Elf is expected
OL,8,Fto fetch up to #200,000 at auction.
OL,10,FBuddy the elf's iconic green, white,
OL,11,Fyellow and black outfit will go under
OL,12,Fthe hammer in December as part of a
OL,13,Fmovie memorabilia auction in London.
OL,15,FThe costume - which comes from the
OL,16,Ffilm's producer Jon Berg - was worn by
OL,17,FFerrell in a lift scene, where Buddy
OL,18,Fpushes the buttons to create a
OL,19,FChristmas tree effect.
