OL,3,CIconic costume from Christmas film Elf
OL,4,Cexpected to fetch up to #200,000
OL,6,FThe movie, released in 2003 to
OL,7,Fwidespread critical acclaim, is
OL,8,Fconsidered one of the top Christmas
OL,9,Ffilms of all time.
OL,11,FIn 2021, a similar costume worn by
OL,12,FFerrell in another scene sold for ten
OL,13,Ftimes what was expected - going for
OL,14,F#218,832, instead of between #20,000
OL,15,Fand #30,000.
OL,17,FThere are more than 1,350 items on
OL,18,Fsale at the Propstore Winter
OL,19,FEntertainment Memorabilia Live
OL,20,FAuction, valued at a combined estimate
OL,21,Fof #8 million.
