OL,6,FAnother item going under the hammer is
OL,7,Fa heavily-annotated personal shooting
OL,8,Fscript from Die Hard (1988) which
OL,9,Fbelonged to Alan Rickman.
OL,11,FIt is expected to sell for between
OL,12,F#30,000 and #60,000.
OL,14,FAnother annotated shooting script once
OL,15,Fbelonging to Rickman, who died aged 69
OL,16,Fin 2016, from the Christmas romantic-
OL,17,Fcomedy Love Actually is also set to go
OL,18,Funder the hammer.
